340
00:15:33,166 --> 00:15:34,517
Oui, pourquoi pas.

341
00:15:35,131 --> 00:15:36,681
"À ma nouvelle maman."

342
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:39,809
"Tu es belle,

343
00:15:40,079 --> 00:15:41,101
