00:19:02,205 --> 00:19:03,344
Prends soin de toi.

424
00:19:04,057 --> 00:19:05,176
<i>Namaste</i>

425
00:19:11,376 --> 00:19:13,073
T'es un sociopathe.

426
00:19:13,421 --> 00:19:15,271
C'était mon âme-yoga-soeur.

427
00:19:15,909 --> 00:19:18,032
Ted étant hors jeu,
